node.text:
📷: #TraderJoes Cold Brew Coffee BBQ Sauce on TJ’s All Natural Crate Free Pork Loin Baby Back Ribs • #TJsRecipe Link In Bio •
—
What better to boost the flavor of your #grilledmeats than BBQ sauce? And what better to boost the flavor your BBQ sauce than… coffee? Yes, #COFFEE!
•
This just-for-summer Sauce has a classic, sweet-tangy base, that is amped up with #coldbrewcoffee concentrate and a custom blend of savory seasonings. Distinct notes of coffee enliven the molasses-y #marinade, as does the combination of spices & herbs, including dried garlic & onion, cumin, oregano, chile de arbol powder, and smoked paprika.
•
👉🏾How will you use our Cold Brew Coffee #BBQSauce?
—
• 19.2 oz. Jar • Limited • 3mg Caffeine Per 2 Tbsp. •

node.text:
Our #CacioEPepe Pasta Sauce—literally, “cheese and pepper”—features Pecorino Romano cheese (from sheep’s milk), and cracked black pepper. Its velvety, zesty character makes an awesome alternate for tomato sauce and an ideal complement for just about any #noodle…
•
Heat and toss with Cappellini, or TJ’s Organic Brown Rice & Quinoa #Spaghetti. Serve it with Fusilli, Penne, or Spinach Tortellini. You can also try layering this #pastasauce between our no-boil #Lasagna Noodles with fresh mozzarella & ricotta for a supremely #cheesy, pleasingly #piquant dish!
•
👉🏼What #TraderJoes pasta will YOU pair with it?
—
• 14.5 oz. Jar • Heat & Eat • Product of Italy 🇮🇹 •

node.text:
📷: “Coconut Limeade,” with #TraderJoes Fresh Squeezed Limeade • #TJsRecipe Link In Bio •
—
If you want #freshsqueezed limeade, you can certainly gather a bunch of #limes and some sugar and squeeze the stuff yourself, though you may end up with a sticky mess before your done. Or you could probably find some at a store—but that version would very likely include high-fructose corn syrup and reconstituted #limejuice from concentrate.
•
A better option is to swing by our refrigerators and pick up a bottle of TJ’s Limeade. Our recipe is simple, with filtered water, sugar, plus fresh lime & lemon juices—not from concentrate. And this beverage is not pasteurized, allowing the pure, sweet-tart #Limeade flavor to shine through. It’s the closest thing to homemade, and all you have to do is shake, open, and pour!
—
• 32 fl. oz. Bottle • Excellent Source of Vitamin C •
• Not Pasteurized • Find It In Our Refrigerators •

node.text:
The 10.8 oz. package of #TraderJoes Gluten Free English Muffins contains four, fluffy, pre-sliced #EnglishMuffins made using a flour blend that includes tapioca starch, rice flour, and chickpea flour.
•
They’re baked in that classic style, with a spongy, #glutenfree crumb characterized by lovely little “pockets & crevices.” The exterior is less of a ‘crust’ and more like a smooth skin that’s lightly dusted with yellow cornmeal.
•
Toast them up for #breakfast. They make an ideal accompaniment for any kind of eggs. Or warm one up when you’re feeling snacky and spread it with one of our fruit Preserves. We even found them to be an excellent delivery system for freshly grilled #burgers!

node.text:
🍍Pleasingly pineapple-y, ultra-fizzy, and subtly sweet, #TraderJoes Sparkling Green Tea with Pineapple Juice sips like a sparkling summer afternoon. 
•
Its earthy backbone of brewed #greentea is accented with the vividly sweet, slighty tart tones of #pineapplejuice. And it’s all delivered with a refreshing effervescence. 
•
We recommend enjoying it chilled, right out of the can. It’s also nice in a glass over ice, or with a handful of TJ’s frozen #Pineapple Tidbits. Perhaps a garnish of mint and fresh pineapple, too? A-lo-HA!
—
• 4 – 8.45 fl. oz. Cans • Product of Vietnam 🇻🇳•
• Pasteurized • Just 2g Sugar & 10 Calories Per Can •

node.text:
🥤#TJsMilkshakeContest WINNERS🥤
• Link In Bio for RECIPES •
—
[1] GRAND PRIZE – @foodisafourletterword
📷: “Mocha Crunch Cake Milkshake” 
[2] 1st RUNNER UP – @simplyyum_blog
📷: “Banana Caramel Wafer Milkshake” 
[3] 2nd RUNNER UP – @cheeseypeasy 
📷: “Hawaiian Whipped Pineapple Shake”
—
We asked customers to create a shake using five TJ’s ingredients, and to post a photo on Instagram for a chance to win up to $200 in TJ’s Gift Cards. 
•
You churned out some legen-dairy (and non-dairy) recipes that were far from homogenized—with inventive ingredients, such as goat cheese, seaweed, jalapeños, and Alfredo sauce. (Explore them all at #TJsMilkshakeContest.)
•
But we couldn’t just kowtow to creativity, with photos and taste to consider. So taste, we did, and the cream rose to the top… In fact, “Mocha Crunch Cake Milkshake” was selected unanimously by our panel as the Grand Prize winner!
—
👉🏽 Visit traderjoes.com for ingredients & directions to make these #milkshakes yourself. 🛒

node.text:
📷: #TraderJoes Organic Ketchup & Organic Yellow Mustard on TJ’s Turkey #CornDogs •
—
When it comes to ketchup, we’ve put our best #condiment-foot forward, starting with organic vine-ripened California #tomatoes, organic cane sugar, and organic distilled vinegar. A custom blend of organic spices, such as onion powder, allspice, red pepper, and paprika helps support the sweet & tangy profile and create the very best #ketchup we could muster! 
•
Speaking of muster… our Organic #YellowMustard is similarly special, including organic grain vinegar, organic #mustard seed, salt, sugar, and some other secret spices. It has that wonderfully bright-yellow hue (thank you, turmeric!), plus just the right amount of mustardy tang for topping #hotdogs, dipping TJ’s Big Soft #Pretzels, or for mixing into your summer #potatosalad.
—
• Organic • Kosher • Under $2 Each • 🔴🟡

node.text:
📷: “Tropical #Mimosa,” featuring Organic Orange Strawberry Banana Juice • #TJsRecipe Link In Bio •
—
Orange, strawberry, and banana sounds like a smoothie combination. But inasmuch as smoothies are thick and shake-like, #TraderJoes Organic Orange Strawberry Banana Juice is aptly named…  and it’s a deliciously refreshing and thirst-quenching #juice!
•
In fact, the 1.5L carton contains six #juices, some from concentrate, some not. Organic purees of banana and strawberry are mixed with four #organicjuices, including orange, apple, pineapple, and white grape to strike just the right balance of tanginess & sweetness—with 0g added sugar.
—
• 100% Juice • High In Vitamin C • Pasteurized •

node.text:
📷: Boatswain Double I.P.A.* paired with “Wedge Salad Dip” • #TJsRecipe Link In Bio • ⚓️
—
In the nautical world, a #boatswain (pronounced: BO-sun) is the petty officer of a ship who is in charge of all that happens on deck. In the world of #TraderJoes, Boatswain is a line of beers we’ve sold for a boatload of years…
•
Among our ‘deckhands,’ Boatswain Double I.P.A. is the most reliably robust. The amber-hued brew is made exclusively for us by an award-winning #craftbrewery that uses #Citra, Cascade, and Eureka #hops to create its rich bitterness, which is beautifully balanced by a handful of carefully selected malts.
•
Even if you scour the seven seas, we’re confident you’ll not find a #DoubleIPA of this stature at such a value—until you reach the friendly port of Trader Joe’s!
—
• 6 pack – 12 fl. oz. Cans • 8.4% Alcohol By Volume •
* Available at Trader Joe’s stores where beer is sold

node.text:
Food lovers have long made culinary companions of figs & olives. Following in this tradition, we’ve combined fruity, sweet #figs with briny, savory #olives in our Fig & Olive Crisps…
•
These flour & buttermilk-based mini-toasts have a healthy crunch, further enhanced by flax, sesame, and sunflower seeds. Dried #Missionfigs from California and brined #Kalamataolives from Greece are evenly distributed throughout to provide that classic, sweet-savory contrast.
•
Try them with a dip in your favorite TJ’s #hummus, or a spread of #Chevre with Honey. Creamy Salted #AlmondButter also pairs surprisingly well. Of course, you can always gild the proverbial lily with a scoop of TJ’s Olive #Tapenade and a slice of whatever fresh figs are seasonal!
—
• Since 2014 • About 55 Crisps • Product of Canada 🇨🇦 •

node.text:
🌶🧀 This #PimentoCheese Dip is our own take on a Southern classic! It includes the requisite ingredients—cheese, #pimentos, and mayo—but we’ve really made it our own with a few upgrades…
•
First, the foundation is real #Cheddar, versus a more processed cheese. And this Cheddar is not just blended with mayo, but also with a #Neufchâtel-like cream cheese, which increases spreadability and contributes another layer of cheesiness.
•
Perhaps most pioneering are our #pickled pimentos that have been brined in white wine vinegar with salt & pepper, garlic, onion, and cayenne. This #pickling imparts a slight, tangy kick that plays well with the sharpness of the Cheddar and ultimately makes this Dip irrezestible!

👉🏻Tell us how you’re going to use #TraderJoes Pimento Cheese Dip…

node.text:
🍦We stock a sweet selection of #HoldTheCone! Mini #IceCreamCone flavors, including Vanilla, Chocolate, and Chocolate Chip—not to mention seasonal options, like Coffee Bean, Pumpkin-Ginger, and Peppermint. But these new Hold The Dairy! Cones are our very first vegan option!
•
Each of the 12 miniature #wafflecones is lined with smooth vegan #chocolate and neatly packed with a coconut-milk-based, chocolate frozen dessert that’s studded with bits of more #veganchocolate. The cone is crunchy, the #dessert is “creamy,” and the whole vegan mini-cone experience is a big deal… especially when you’re eating #dairyfree!
—
• Non-Dairy • Vegan • Product of Italy 🇮🇹 •
